<P>
The recent "Eye on L.A." program on Chile was a disgrace! Not only did it 
mispronounce half of the city's names, but it portrayed Chile as the "fashion 
capital of the world." Chile has always been known for its culture, not for its 
designers! 
</P>
<P>
Alicia Matricardi, Los Angeles 
