<TEXT>
<P>
It is with an extreme sense of ironic incredulity that I view Abramson. She 
makes the statement about being "bathed in the backwash of the Holocaust," yet 
she defends those whose crimes are no less heinous than the vile, Nazi thugs 
she deplores. One wonders if she would have been so charitable at Nuremburg. 
</P>
<P>
MATTHEW L. DADAY 
</P>
<P>
Torrance 
</P>
