<P>
PROBATION; CAMPS; GANGS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; JUVENILE CRIMINALS; THEATER; 
CREATIVITY; FIREBIRD THEATER COMPANY; GRANTS; REHABILITATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
