with sidekick Ed McMahon) holds firm to his No. 1 rating in late-night 
television. United Press International; Photo, The Crown Prince: Arsenio Hall 
has become one of the top players in the late-night competition since his 
syndicated show began last January. Here Hall greets comedian-actor Eddie 
