<P>
PASKOWITZ ADVANCES IN LONGBOARDING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
OCEANSIDE 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Israel Paskowitz of San Clemente advanced Saturday to the semifinal round in 
two divisions in the Oceanside Longboard Surfing Club contest. 
</P>
<P>
Paskowitz advanced in the noserider and the young men's (19-29) divisions. 
Highly regarded noserider Chris Schlickenmeyer of Hawaii failed to advance. 
</P>
