<TEXT>
<P>
Altadena artifact -- A headline and photo caption in the Aug. 24 Times 
incorrectly identified the location in Altadena where an ancient Indian 
grinding stone was found. The artifact was found near a proposed residential 
housing development, not on the development site. 
</P>
